hass-optimized-pulse-meter

This project contains code derived from ESPHome's pulse_meter component.

ESPHome license summary, as stated by the ESPHome project:
- C++/runtime code (.c, .cpp, .h, .hpp, .tcc, .ino): GPLv3
- Python code and other parts: MIT

Original project:
  ESPHome
  https://github.com/esphome/esphome

Derived component:
  esphome/components/pulse_meter

Modifications in this repository include:
- Renaming the component to optimized_pulse_meter.
- Adding flow_lambda for frequency-to-value conversion.
- Adding volume_lambda for per-pulse volume accumulation.
- Adding max_time_delta clamping for per-pulse interval handling.
- Clamping negative, NaN, and infinite lambda outputs to zero.

No warranty is provided. Validate measurements against known references before relying on them.
